{"tid":2015570,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"(又重製)《四海兄弟：決定版》遊戲上架微軟商城實機截圖震撼無比！","createTime":"2020-05-13T18:51:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-14T17:53:27.000Z","uid":215755,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0fc143520fca775ff35514a53de7805b97f621c5","tid":2015570,"uid":215755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T18:51:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1shVYF9nBMk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D1shVYF9nBMk&d=xUEPa7L8eIFrsai6sDUjHM2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=73bd09bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1shVYF9nBMk</a><br />\n<br />\n5月13日晚上《四海兄弟》官方公佈了一支《四海兄弟3：三部曲》預告，視頻並沒有透露太多信息，只是表示會在5月20日帶來新消息。而現在驚喜來了！《四海兄弟：決定版》與《四海兄弟2：決定版》已經上架微軟商城，從截圖能看《四海兄弟：決定版》是不折不扣的&ldquo;完全重製&rdquo;遊戲，畫面效果非常之震撼。<br />\n<br />\n作為《四海兄弟》系列遊戲的粉絲，筆者第一眼看到《四海兄弟：決定版》的截圖時，心中充滿了各種感嘆詞。這款2002年的經典遊戲經過完全重製後，畫面效果堪稱次世代。猜測本作可能是採用了《四海兄弟3》引擎的升級版進行了重製。<br />\n<br />\n《四海兄弟：決定版》的商店頁面還顯示，本作會迎來新的故事內容，看來製作組不僅僅是重製了畫面，還在遊戲流程上給玩家帶來了不少驚喜。頁面顯示遊戲將在2020年8月28日發售。<br />\n<br />\n此外，《四海兄弟2：決定版》相比原版遊戲畫面也有了明顯提升，但似乎沒有達到《四海兄弟：決定版》那麼驚豔的效果，官方也只是將其描述為&ldquo;高清化&rdquo;。微軟商城顯示本作會在2020年5月19日發售。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r3TFzMi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr3TFzMi.jpg&h=e49eba9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/28Tm3ED.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F28Tm3ED.jpg&h=5c5703ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MRwoxxZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMRwoxxZ.jpg&h=33d6f062&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uKUacxZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuKUacxZ.jpg&h=e1f912ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kXDm3EF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkXDm3EF.jpg&h=95c407a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8hpacx1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8hpacx1.jpg&h=141da238&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c8a92c4ad13ffc06b1599b99570afde32bebad3f","tid":2015570,"uid":50601,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T18:57:08.000Z","msg":"第二集真係好玩到仆街 個故事 最後個ending 更加係接返第一集 真係神作"},{"pid":"31e75c55d0a7046ea7bf58d08f22e860356f887c","tid":2015570,"uid":215755,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"c8a92c4ad13ffc06b1599b99570afde32bebad3f","tid":2015570,"uid":50601,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T18:57:08.000Z","msg":"第二集真係好玩到仆街 個故事 最後個ending 更加係接返第一集 真係神作"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T19:08:33.000Z","msg":"第二集比發售前D FAKE NEWS累死咗<br />\n仲記得D人吹到隻GAME自由度大過GTA十倍又可以自由結婚生仔結果隻GAME一出好多人屌鬼,但本身唔差<br />\n第三集純粹睇Vito同Joe結局, D物理同BUG搞死咗隻GAME"},{"pid":"598bacc423f9203b1276b5c6eff55cb1d48aed6a","tid":2015570,"uid":33357,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T20:22:39.000Z","msg":"Mafia 2好正<br />\n3就變左垃圾"},{"pid":"cd9df5be7f2130848d47d17c16e856c2fd9e9740","tid":2015570,"uid":72749,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T20:56:15.000Z","msg":"vito!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c01d4fcb7febd11f9d567764402c99f2a957113","tid":2015570,"uid":36248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T22:52:35.000Z","msg":"早幾年有玩番第一集 <br />\n正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64d40ef181288405044a0fee0521fdd594904c58","tid":2015570,"uid":56731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T23:23:05.000Z","msg":"如果R星用依個年代整返隻黑手黨GAME就仲正"},{"pid":"c5931230d1314d48aa8b3a0db1e7935cc29b6980","tid":2015570,"uid":151364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T23:27:16.000Z","msg":"第一集remake<img src=\"/assets/fa